data.description: Do you need space?  Do you want a move in ready home that is practically brand new? This is the home for you!  Located in Shawnee School District, this 3 bedroom (4th bedroom in basement) has been completely updated!  We're talking new windows, flooring, appliances, water heater, fencing, kitchen, bathrooms . . . to much to mention.  Call myself or your favorite agent for a complete list of updates and schedule a showing to see this beautiful home for yourself.
